title: Bananarchy's FNV Mod Box
description:
This is mostly graphical and immersion mods, although there are plenty of content mods in there too
All credit is given to modders in the included readme
Don't be intimidated by the file-size, 3/4 of that is a texture pack
This mod will NOT install them for you, although there is a readme with clear insstructions on how to do so
This is 100% legal, so seed
